text:
Madam...
TA lab mai gandhi ke sath mile the or ek formailty wala project bana dala tha pr bad mai enviro ki lab mai hangout krte the or last sems mai to Civil Shakti ne hi pass kraya.
Shashwat ke sare comments lene ke lie aur unn video calls ko funny bnane ke lie shukriya!!
Fr milenge!
author: Bhavesh  Loungani

text:
Sir Sir bolkr hmesha bkchodi krna koi apse sikhe.....
Civil ka name uncha krne ke liye aabhaar...  Intern se phle ke randirone or phukan ko dii hui gaaliyan nahi bhul skta mai...Nomura ke pure staff ko gaali deta tha tu chahe sakshi ho ya gaurav....Pr bhai mza aa gaya tha jab ppo ki news mili
Cheating ke bhrose dusro se jyada number laane wale haraami....
Mumbai mai milte bhai
author: Bhavesh  Loungani

text:
Ankur bhai....tjhe kabhi nahi bhul skta mai
Ankur sweet hai and anukant mc hai...
Bhot sari chize yad aa rhi hai isliye sb kuch likh deta hu...
Sbse phle to thanks meri itni sari batein sunne ke lie jab mai out of control ho jata hu....mne nahi socha tha ki itne se time mai itni achi dosti ho jaegi.
Sath mai itne sare rolls, shakes, biryani, or na jane kya kya khaya hai....Bc kitni achi maggi bnata tha mai 
Bhai sbse important bat likh deta hu jo shyd apn dono hi smjhte hai ki khushboo 5th dimension hoti hai and uske aate hi mza aa jata hai...
baki bhai bhot gehri batein kari hai.....A2, A3, A6 koi rooftop nahi chhoda tha....you must admit last tk aate aate mai bhot jaldi saaf kr deta tha....mjhe exoertise dilane ke lie thanks
Apne biryani se phle wale sessions, sanket ke bday wale din ki chocolate and GOT dekhte dekhte chair pr so jana hmesha yaad rhega bhai....
Bhot late mile lekin bhot ache mile apn...
Finally, there will come a day when the courage of men fails.........
.......but today is not that day, tonight we fight<3

Milte hai bhai jaldi hi!!  cheers!!
author: Bhavesh  Loungani

text:
Ankunant!
bhai log galat khte hai tu mze nahi leta logo ke, wo bhand hote hai isliye esa khte hai, tu mast aadmi hai
Hmesha welcoming rhne ke lie thanks, apna charger dene ke lie dhanyawaad, anubha ke quiz wali subah yaad hai na?
Baki to bhai apn dono hi kum frequency wale log the isliye mai kehta tha ki jis din mai aaunga uss din to tjhe bhi aana hoga....apn dono hi to noob hai group ke haha
Bkchod gaane gaaye hai tune bhai; mza aa jata tha yar tere or sanket ke sath baith kr, not to forget ankur ka tabla.....bhai jaldi hi milte hai and recreate krte hai
author: Bhavesh  Loungani

text:
Gandhi bhai...
Degree dilwane ke lie dhanyawaad...yaad bhi nahi ki kitne topics pdhaye hai tune, kitne exams mai cheating krayi and kitne courses pass krwaye
Uske alawa bhi hmesha saath dia bhai...IME project mai sath mai kuch nahi kia tha, TA project mai sath mai gand mrayi thi, library mi sath finance pdha tha, barclays mai sath mai ktaya tha, bc resume ke projects bhi sare same the or fr dono jakr OYO mai hi phasee
BC kitni chize hai sari likh bhi nahi paunga.....civil ki labs mai kitni maa chudai hai, environmental mai pura time bkchodi kaati thi ,  intern pr OYO ko gaali dete the, flipkart ki deck discuss krte the
Placement season mai mere randi rone sunne ke lie koi nahi tha pr tjhpr trust tha bhai....jb bhi frust hota tha to tjhe text kr leta tha and sari companies ko gaali deta tha tere samne
Bad mai bhi 7th 8th semester mai sare courses tere hi bhrose the...pata tha ki kuch bhi hoga to tu jo bolega wo mark krna hai 
Ye likh deta hu taki tjhe yad rhe ki tune uss din mjhe apna peg pilaya tha kyuki tu to bhand tha, pata nahi abhi yaad bhi hoga xD
Ye memoir ki wse hume jrurt pdni nahi chahiye kyuki abhi bhot lmba jana hai...
Goa ki trip baki hai and
Mumbai mai kitab likhne jitne kaand krne hai <3
Tab tk chill marta reh and logo ki help krta reh!!
author: Bhavesh  Loungani

text:
Sir Pranaam!!
Ajay ya shashwat ki wajah se hi mile the prr dheere dheere kafi batein hone lagi thi. Bhot positive banda hai yar tu, isliye hmesha sahi rha tere sath hangout krna, teri intern ke bare mai shyd hmari bat na hui ho pr mne tera example bhot logo ko chipkaya hai and khud bhi inspire hua tha usse....
Uske bad to hmesha bhaiya ke jokes pr hasna yad hai aur google meet pr cheating krna.
Axis ka result aate hi mne sbse phle tjhe hi call kia tha pr tune phle hi guess krlia isliye mai mze nahi le paya.
SSAC lgne ki bat pr sbse phle tjhe hi phone kia tha, ye sochkr ki tu bacha lega pr acha hua uski jrurt nhi padi
Last din bhi sahi tha yar, or aage aane wale dino ke lie sahi foundation set krdi thi.....Jaldi hi milte hai mumbai mai
Api positivity and creativity bacha kr rkhna...cheers bhai
author: Bhavesh  Loungani

text: bhot lmba memoir likhna hai , tb tk ke lye isse visible krde
author: Bhavesh  Loungani

text:
prakhar ka kanpuriya dost.....
1st year se hi tmhari bkchodi dekh rhe or usse enjoy kr rhe hai..
Pr turning point to wo 2nd year summers mai yaad hai jab mai SAE workshop m aa gaya tha or bc apnne pata nahi kyu pr duniya bhar ki batein kari thi; uss din ki kuch batei mjhe abhi bhi yaad hai and ab bhi help krti hai.....tbhi se lga tha ki sahi bnde ho tum 
Uske bad to civil ke courses mai class mai teacher ki nakl krna, DC Rai ki acting, mobile se cheating krna sikhaya.....bhot mze kraye hai bhai tune
7th 8th sem ke sare video calls mai madam ki hansi udana aur sbke mze lena hmesha ka kaam hota tha tmhara....
Last din to meri bat nahi maane the pr agr agle saal tk nashe shuru ho jae to btana!!
author: Bhavesh  Loungani
